  "text": "The research objectives determine the method to be used in data analysis. In past research, several authors have used linear regression to study adolescents' influence on family buying decisions (Mangleburg et al. 1999, Beatty and [CITATION_1] . However, there is no knowledge of the use of logistic regression in the study of adolescents' influence on family purchasing decisions. The reasons for choosing logistic regression analysis in this study are the variables' level of measurement and the explained variable characteristics.",
